irth:1 CONT Place of Birth: Dundee1 CONT Address: 6 Marybank Lane, Lochee.1 CONT Occupation: Linoleum Worker1 CONT Mother:1 CONT Father:1 CONT Siblings:1 CONT Spouse: Ellen Farrell, 6 Marybank Lane, Lochee1 CONT Children:1 CONT More about Jones Munro1 CONT Jones has no known grave but is remembered on the Menin Gate Memorial.1 CONT1 CONT Jones Munro    292946   Black Watch1 CONT1 CONT LOCHEE SPORTSMAN KILLED IN ACTION.1 CONT1 CONT Private Jones Munro, Black Watch, whose wife resides at 6 Marybank Lane, was 33 years of age, and was a linoleum worker at Liff prior to enlisting in February, 1915.  He had been thirteen months in France.  Deceased was well known in junior football circl1 CONC es, having played for three years in the Dundee West End and for one year in the Dundee Harp.1 CONT1 CONT Dundee Courier 21st August 19171 CHAN2 DATE 13 MAR 20223 TIME 23:47:381 _CRE2 DATE 13 MAR 20223 TIME 23:44:070 @86902428@ NOTE1 CONT https://theblackwatch.co.uk/blog/roll-of-honour/roll-of-honour-818/1 CONT1 CONT Notes as Jones Munro1 CHAN2 DATE 13 MAR 20223 TIME 23:57:001 _CRE2 DATE 13 MAR 20223 TIME 23:47:380 @6503712@ NOTE1 CONT 18681 CONT Castlebar, Ireland1 CHAN2 DATE 05 JUN 20223 TIME 15:30:431 _CRE2 DATE 05 JUN 20223 TIME 15:30:400 @70098680@ NOTE1 CONT 1851 Census1 CHAN2 DATE 20 AUG 20243 TIME 17:41:031 _CRE2 DATE 20 AUG 20243 TIME 17:40:550 @1248096@ NOTE1 CONT 1891 census1 CHAN2 DATE 16 APR 20223 TIME 11:28:321 _CRE2 DATE 16 APR 20223 TIME 11:28:250 @19240492@ NOTE1 CONT unknown source1 CONT1 CONT 16 October 18901 CONT 27 Polepark Road, Lochee, Dundee, Angus, Scotland1 CONT1 CONT1 CHAN2 DATE 21 FEB 20223 TIME 21:29:481 _CRE2 DATE 21 FEB 20223 TIME 21:26:560 @52144076@ NOTE1 CONT <ref>1 CONT '''Birth''':1 CONT "Scotland, Select Births and Baptisms, 1564-1950"<br/>1 CONT Original data: Scotland, Births and Baptisms, 1564-1950. Salt Lake City, Utah: FamilySearch, 2013<br/>1 CONT {{Ancestry Reco